## FTS5 Search Tests

```rust
#[test]
fn test_fts_search_basic() {
    let (graph, _tmp) = create_test_graph();

    let id = ObjectBuilder::character("Saruman".to_string())
        .add_to_graph(&graph)
        .unwrap();

    graph.add_text_chunk(
        id,
        "Saruman the White was head of the Istari order.".to_string(),
        ChunkType::Description,
    ).unwrap();

    // Keyword present
    let hits = graph.search_chunks_fts("Istari", 5).unwrap();
    assert_eq!(hits.len(), 1);
    assert_eq!(hits[0].1, id);

    // Keyword absent
    let empty = graph.search_chunks_fts("dragon", 5).unwrap();
    assert!(empty.is_empty());
}
```

FTS5 query syntax supported: phrase (`"foo bar"`), prefix (`foo*`), boolean
(`foo AND bar`, `foo OR bar`, `foo NOT bar`), column filters.

