## CI Commands

```bash
cargo fmt --check
cargo clippy -- -D warnings
cargo test -- --test-threads=1
cargo doc --no-deps
cargo run --example cli_demo
```

No `source env.sh` required. No model downloads. All commands work offline.

Integration tests are automatically skipped when no Lemonade Server is reachable
(localhost probe finds nothing and `LEMONADE_URL` is unset). Always pass
`--test-threads=1` — integration tests share GPU/NPU hardware on the server and
must not run concurrently.

Transcription integration tests (`test_lemonade_transcribe_*`) require
`whisper-v3-turbo-FLM` to be pulled on the server. They are automatically
skipped when no server is reachable.